@WebApplication1_HostAddress = http://localhost:5004

### Pobierz wszystkie sale
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms
Accept: application/json

### Pobierz salę po id
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms/1
Accept: application/json

### Pobierz sale z budynku A
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms/building/A
Accept: application/json

### Filtrowanie po query stringu
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms?minCapacity=20&hasProjector=true&activeOnly=true
Accept: application/json

### Dodaj nową salę
POST {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lab 999",
  "buildingCode": "C",
  "floor": 2,
  "capacity": 30,
  "hasProjector": true,
  "isActive": true
}

### Aktualizuj salę
PUT {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lab 101 Updated",
  "buildingCode": "A",
  "floor": 1,
  "capacity": 25,
  "hasProjector": false,
  "isActive": true
}

### Usuń salę
DELETE {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/rooms/1